Configure TeXstudio for output: 

Options -> Configure TeXstudio -> Commands -> pdflatex 
and add -output-directory=output

pdflatex -synctex=1 -interaction=nonstopmode -output-directory=output %.tex

then go to
Options -> Configure TeXstudio -> build -> Show Advanced Options 
then add under Log file the folder o

pdflatex -synctex=1 -interaction=nonstopmode -output-directory=output %.tex
evince output/%.pdf > /dev/null
bibtex output/%.aux
makeglossaries -d output %

Log File: output
PDF File: output

Build & View
txs:///compile | txs:///bibtex | txs:///makeglossaries | txs:///compile | txs:///view
